subject: ENGLISH
text: Write a Composition, not exceeding three foolscap pages in length, on any one of the following subjects:

subject: ENGLISH
text: A character sketch of an old shepherd, or an old fisherman, or an old gardener, or an old pavement artist.

subject: ENGLISH
text: What past age in Scotland would you most like to have lived in, and why?

subject: ENGLISH
text: Does every change in fashion necessarily imply an improvement in taste?
